474
00:29:11,270 --> 00:29:13,780
<font color=#FFFF00>Hei, kau harus mengingatnya!</font>

475
00:29:14,410 --> 00:29:15,610
<font color=#FFFF00>Oppa.</font>

476
00:29:17,250 --> 00:29:19,180
<font color=#FFFF00>Ada apa? Kami belum menemukan apa-apa.</font>

477
00:29:19,180 --> 00:29:22,050
<font color=#FFFF00>- Sudah kubilang akan meneleponmu kalau ada.
- Bisa kita bicara sebentar?</font>

478
00:29:31,390 --> 00:29:34,860
<font color=#FFFF00>Permen Karet, aku tahu kau khawatir.
Aku pasti akan menelepon kalau menemukan sesuatu.</font>

479
00:29:41,170 --> 00:29:42,440
<font color=#FFFF00>Joon Oppa.</font>

480
00:29:43,140 --> 00:29:44,270
<font color=#FFFF00>Kenapa?</font>

481
00:29:47,640 --> 00:29:48,710
<font color=#FFFF00>"Kenapa"?</font>

482
00:29:56,180 --> 00:29:57,590
<font color=#FFFF00>Dasar tidak tahu malu!</font>

483
00:30:08,000 --> 00:30:09,330
<font color=#FFFF00>Joon Oppa-ku...</font>

484
00:30:11,130 --> 00:30:12,570
<font color=#FFFF00>Sungguh sudah mati?</font>

485
00:30:13,840 --> 00:30:15,140
<font color=#FFFF00>Apa dia sungguh sudah mati?</font>

486
00:30:24,010 --> 00:30:25,880
<font color=#FFFF00>- Itu...
- Dia mati atau tidak?</font>

487
00:30:37,260 --> 00:30:38,390
<font color=#FFFF00>Benar, tapi...</font>

488
00:30:40,230 --> 00:30:41,900
<font color=#FFFF00>Dasar bajingan jahat!</font>

489
00:31:03,490 --> 00:31:06,820
<font color=#FFFF00>Kesalahan macam apa yang sudah dia perbuat sampai
ditampar oleh gadis itu?</font>

490
00:31:08,260 --> 00:31:10,990
<font color=#FFFF00>Aiyoo... dia pasti habis membuat masalah.</font>

491
00:31:12,660 --> 00:31:13,760
<font color=#FFFF00>Apa?</font>

492
00:31:18,630 --> 00:31:19,700
<font color=#FFFF00>Astaga.</font>

493
00:31:20,870 --> 00:31:21,870
<font color=#FFFF00>Anak ini...</font>

494
00:31:23,450 --> 00:31:25,280
<font color=#FFFF00>- Hei.
- Ini.</font>

495
00:31:27,520 --> 00:31:28,920
<font color=#FFFF00>Ah, benar, dia.</font>

496
00:31:28,920 --> 00:31:32,190
<font color=#FFFF00>Aey, tapi kenapa Moo Gang memiliki foto anak ini?</font>

497
00:31:37,600 --> 00:31:38,860
<font color=#FFFF00><i>Han Moo Gang?</i></font>

498
00:31:39,630 --> 00:31:41,430
<font color=#FFFF00><i>Sedang apa berandal itu di sana?</i></font>

499
00:31:41,700 --> 00:31:43,970
<font color=#FFFF00>Hari itu, Han Moo Gang pergi menemui keparat itu.</font>

500
