526
00:32:51,170 --> 00:32:53,840
<font color=#FFFF00>Ya, apa kira-kira Anda tahu soal apa itu?</font>

527
00:32:53,840 --> 00:32:57,780
<font color=#FFFF00>Ya. Kakaknya meninggal di Moojin.</font>

528
00:32:57,780 --> 00:32:58,910
<font color=#FFFF00>Di Moojin?</font>

529
00:32:58,910 --> 00:32:59,980
<font color=#FFFF00>Ya.</font>

530
00:32:59,980 --> 00:33:02,850
<font color=#FFFF00>Saya harus menghadiri sebuah seminar di Moojin...</font>

531
00:33:03,120 --> 00:33:05,980
<font color=#FFFF00>...dan hari itu anak-anak sedang bebas jam sekolah,</font>

532
00:33:05,980 --> 00:33:08,520
<font color=#FFFF00>jadi saya mengajak mereka bersama saya.</font>

533
00:33:08,520 --> 00:33:10,790
<font color=#FFFF00><i>Batu-kertas-gunting. Batu-kertas-gunting!</i></font>

534
00:33:10,890 --> 00:33:12,290
<font color=#FFFF00><i>Batu-kertas-gunting.</i></font>

