537
00:33:18,030 --> 00:33:21,630
<font color=#FFFF00><i>Anak-anak, lihat ke sini. Kalungkan lengan kalian satu sama lain.</i></font>

538
00:33:22,330 --> 00:33:24,070
<font color=#FFFF00><i>Lihat sini.</i></font>

