546
00:33:58,070 --> 00:33:59,270
<font color=#FFFF00><i>Halo?</i></font>

547
00:34:00,370 --> 00:34:01,940
<font color=#FFFF00><i>Ah, Moo Gang-ah. Sedang apa kalian?</i></font>

548
00:34:02,570 --> 00:34:05,940
