551
00:34:11,680 --> 00:34:13,920
<font color=#FFFF00><i>Ajak kakakkmu berkeliling Moojin.</i></font>

552
00:34:14,050 --> 00:34:15,490
<font color=#FFFF00><i>Sampai jumpa nanti.</i></font>

553
00:34:16,760 --> 00:34:18,760
<font color=#FFFF00><i>Sebentar, apa yang terjadi?</i></font>

554
00:34:18,760 --> 00:34:19,860
