643
00:39:43,920 --> 00:39:47,150
<font color=#FFFF00><i>Jin Sook juga menghilang setelahnya.</i></font>

644
00:39:47,150 --> 00:39:52,490
<font color=#FFFF00>Tubuh Woo Byung Sik ditemukan 19 April 1997.</font>

645
00:39:59,600 --> 00:40:00,900
<font color=#FFFF00>Berarti,</font>

646
00:40:02,070 --> 00:40:04,840
<font color=#FFFF00>Clara, Han Jin Sook, dan Kim Sun Young, semuanya menghilang...</font>

647
00:40:05,270 --> 00:40:08,370
<font color=#FFFF00>...pada sore hari tanggal 19 April 1997.</font>

648
00:40:10,040 --> 00:40:13,250
<font color=#FFFF00>Dan mayat kakaknya Han Moo Gang ditemukan...</font>

649
00:40:13,250 --> 00:40:16,210
<font color=#FFFF00>...keesokan hari tanggal 20 April pukul 4 pagi.</font>

650
00:40:19,580 --> 00:40:22,550
<font color=#FFFF00>Clara ditemukan tewas di pabrik ini.</font>

651
00:40:22,550 --> 00:40:25,720
<font color=#FFFF00>Dan kakaknya Han Moo Gang ditemukan di jalan ini,</font>

652
00:40:26,730 --> 00:40:29,930
<font color=#FFFF00>yang hanya berjarak 1,1 kilometer dari pabrik.</font>

653
00:40:31,100 --> 00:40:32,430
<font color=#FFFF00>1,1 kilometer.</font>

