<font color=#FFFF00>Ah, Kepolisian Moojin?</font>

656
00:40:47,310 --> 00:40:49,250
<font color=#FFFF00>Oh, Detektif Choi. Ini aku.</font>

657
00:40:49,820 --> 00:40:51,080
<font color=#FFFF00>Hei, tolong bantu aku.</font>

658
00:40:51,920 --> 00:40:54,290
<font color=#FFFF00>Jika kau memeriksa dokumen yang sudah habis waktu
