00:43:14,730 --> 00:43:16,090
<font color=#FFFF00><i>Joon Oppa.</i></font>

678
00:43:19,930 --> 00:43:21,230
<font color=#FFFF00><i>Bajingan itu...</i></font>

679
00:43:21,830 --> 00:43:24,770
<font color=#FFFF00><i>...tahu abunya Joon Oppa disimpan di sini.</i></font>

